{"tid":1526254,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"可唔可以為呢個運動每年開紀念晚會","createTime":"2019-09-01T05:02:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-01T05:05:08.000Z","uid":177801,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"b582523e373fed603f773b09109117482fd26c36","tid":1526254,"uid":177801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T05:02:16.000Z","msg":"發夢發左兩個月<br />\n琴晚發夢差啲喺太子站俾犬打嘅就係我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n覺得好對唔住班義士<br />\n<br />\n大家可唔可以喺呢埸運動完咗之後特定一晚開紀念晚會，就好似六四追悼會咁樣，紀念義士同埋強烈譴責警犬嘅濫權，表達社會對香港警察執法的不滿，好好咁教育下一代<br />\n<br />\n相信經過左呢兩個月 大家對popo嘅怨恨大大提升<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔好俾佢停 因為我哋喺唔會原諒牠們的<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n天佑香港<br />\n今日機場見"},{"pid":"72f2edf6ae5b1bff620cd2c1c00a0f9e38d8667b","tid":1526254,"uid":177801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T05:02:29.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"52abb48db26e110df1eb7e0c406744e14fb3ebf0","tid":1526254,"uid":177801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T05:02:39.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"222f659d42fa309cd1e82b77541df43086bc739c","tid":1526254,"uid":177801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T05:02:49.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"cd83bf783d3ba680d3bcc55f9116ee0be5c20474","tid":1526254,"uid":177336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T05:03:00.000Z","msg":"901 機場攻略<br />\n麻煩大家用盡所有方法傳開佢<br />\n<br />\n- <span style=\"color: red;\">準時</span>到機場，唔係一點先出門口<br />\n- 衣着同裝備冇任何限制，最緊要保護自己<br />\n- 集合地點：機場巴士總站(暢達路)<br />\n- 測試方法：排隊戰術，見到<span style=\"color: red;\">有隊就排</span>；利用人數優勢，<span style=\"color: red;\">唔好單獨行事</span><br />\n- 唔好同任何遊客有肢體碰撞<br />\n- 去機場：<span style=\"color: red;\">以巴士為優先</span>，機場快線集中係香港同青衣站上車<br />\n- 已經準備左幾套應變方案，根據現場情況<span style=\"color: red;\">隨時轉變</span>，要密切留意住 901 機場 Channel<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=dE5eED8%2BMjLqHtNzOSR2Xybpne3YAKjwmabJhOlqIzs%3D&h=0f8b4874\" target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/stuckwithyou</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/P5XusdO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FP5XusdO.jpg&h=31adcd48&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cTXKf68.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcTXKf68.jpg&h=74d57433&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qAxaV7a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqAxaV7a.jpg&h=13c2eb06&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/otZAnNa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FotZAnNa.jpg&h=f10fa124&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a44bb2c3fcab41edaef5433be4022719f8fb0d32","tid":1526254,"uid":177801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T05:03:06.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"c89416404342982ad4eda3d55fe828db151d360f","tid":1526254,"uid":177801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T05:03:16.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"a5fd0208355b8ed486cd1cabb2eec44851f78573","tid":1526254,"uid":177801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T05:03:29.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"640541c227ff6d16fe4c6a364ad629f174347d1d","tid":1526254,"uid":177801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T05:03:41.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"6a535474b0f4ca032d60ed557cc6ffba6265670b","tid":1526254,"uid":177801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T05:03:51.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"75314c6f8a53e94b25c4525d24bfdf2843d14fc7","tid":1526254,"uid":177801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T05:04:07.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"8d350f26442748d5a24640f532c9c12b768ea275","tid":1526254,"uid":177801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T05:04:29.000Z